commits.author: Robert Muir
commits.sourceNew:
/** * Returns the doc values format that should be used for writing * new segments of field. *

* The field to format mapping is written to the index, so * this method is only invoked when writing, not when reading. */ public abstract SimpleDocValuesFormat getDocValuesFormatForField(String field);
